**Implementing the Import Fix**

I'm now implementing the fix: adding `<script type="module" src="./index.tsx"></script>` to `index.html` and updating `index.tsx` to use named import `createRoot` from `react-dom/client`. I'm confirming all imports in `App.tsx` look correct, especially `recharts` and `lucide-react`. I will test to verify the fix works. I'll check for crashes on `App.tsx` on render.


